('en','messages:apihelp-query+filerepoinfo-paramvalue-prop-name','s:189:\"The key of the repository - used in e.g. <var>[[mw:Special:MyLanguage/Manual:$wgForeignFileRepos|$wgForeignFileRepos]]</var> and [[Special:ApiHelp/query+imageinfo|imageinfo]] return values.\";'),
