('en','messages:apiwarn-unclearnowtimestamp','s:194:\"Passing \"$2\" for timestamp parameter <var>$1</var> has been deprecated. If for some reason you need to explicitly specify the current time without calculating it client-side, use <kbd>now</kbd>.\";'),
