('en','messages:clearyourcache','s:538:\"<strong>Note:</strong> After publishing, you may have to bypass your browser\'s cache to see the changes.\n* <strong>Firefox / Safari:</strong> Hold <em>Shift</em> while clicking <em>Reload</em>, or press either <em>Ctrl-F5</em> or <em>Ctrl-R</em> (<em>Ōīś-R</em> on a Mac)\n* <strong>Google Chrome:</strong> Press <em>Ctrl-Shift-R</em> (<em>Ōīś-Shift-R</em> on a Mac)\n* <strong>Internet Explorer / Edge:</strong> Hold <em>Ctrl</em> while clicking <em>Refresh</em>, or press <em>Ctrl-F5</em>\n* <strong>Opera:</strong> Press <em>Ctrl-F5</em>.\";'),
