('en','messages:dante-database-dump-intro','s:137:\"This page allows you to produce a dump of the \'\'\'entire database\'\'\' of this dantewiki. For more information consult [[Help:DanteBackup]].\";'),
('en','messages:dante-page-dump-intro','s:447:\"This page allows you to produce a dump of the \'\'\'content\'\'\' of this dantewiki (read: articles, files, revisions but no user accounts, system messages, system configurations and further so-called meta data). For files, content and upload actions are included. Make sure, File: pages are selected when not dumping all pages. For more information consult [[Help:DanteBackup]]. <b>CAVE:</b> Not all features implemented currently, some features buggy.\";'),
('en','messages:dante-page-restore-intro','s:305:\"This page allows you to restore a dump of the \'\'\'content\'\'\' of this dantewiki (read: articles, files, revisions but no user accounts, system messages, system configurations and further so-called meta data). Please select a file to be used for restoring. For more information consult [[Help:DanteRestore]].\";'),
