('en','messages:expand_templates_intro','s:299:\"This special page takes wikitext and expands all templates in it recursively.\nIt also expands supported parser functions like\n<code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>#language:ŌĆ”}}</code> and variables like\n<code><nowiki>{{</nowiki>CURRENTDAY}}</code>.\nIn fact, it expands pretty much everything in double-braces.\";'),
