('en','messages:filepageexists','s:279:\"The description page for this file has already been created at <strong>[[:$1]]</strong>, but no file with this name currently exists.\nThe summary you enter will not appear on the description page.\nTo make your summary appear there, you will need to manually edit it.\n[[$1|thumb]]\";'),
