('en','messages:interwiki_intro','s:277:\"This is an overview of the interwiki table, which defines the prefix shortcuts used to quickly link to different wikis and other external sites. For recommended use, please see [https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Extension:Interwiki the manual on MediaWiki.org].\";'),
