('en','messages:interwiki_trans_1_intro','s:292:\"If wikitext syntax <code>{<nowiki />{prefix:<em>pagename</em>}}</code> is used, allow template/page transclusion from the foreign wiki if interwiki transclusions are enabled in general ([https://www.mediawiki.org/wiki/Special:MyLanguage/Manual:$wgEnableScaryTranscluding scary transclusion]).\";'),
