('en','messages:treeandmenu-desc','s:373:\"Adds <code><nowiki>#tree</nowiki></code> and <code><nowiki>#menu</nowiki></code> parser functions which contain bullet-lists to be rendered as collapsible treeviews or dropdown menus.\nThe treeviews use the [http://wwwendt.de/tech/fancytree FancyTree] JavaScript tree menu, and the dropdown menus use [http://www.htmldog.com/articles/suckerfish/dropdowns/ Son of Suckerfish]\";'),
