(30,'operational modes',' au800 mediawiki hasu800 tou800 load andu800 compile areu800 large number ofu800 phpu800 files. this takes time sou800 during normal operations this process usually isu800 cached which saves au800 lotu800 ofu800 time foru800 loading andu800 compilation. however during development youu800 dou800 notu800 want theu800 files tou800 beu800 cached butu800 youu800 always want theu800 most recent changes inu800 theu800 source code tou800 beu800 used. thus allu800 files have tou800 beu800 loaded check andu800 ifu800 necessary recompiled. also youu800 might want tou800 seeu800 warning notices about deprecated functions. inu800 au800 wikipedia installation theu800 respective settings usually areu800 done asu800 part ofu800 theu800 setup process. inu800 dantewiki however theu800 developers want tou800 beu800 able tou800 switch quickly between theu800 different modes sou800 that theu800 development cycle ofu800 dantewiki canu800 beu800 faster. theu800 setting canu800 beu800 switched byu800 special debug mode andu800 theu800 currently active mode isu800 displayed inu800 theu800 footer. category danteinitialcontents '),
(31,'danteinitialcontents',' file dblpu82epngu800 file exampleu82esvgu800 file flexu82esvgu800 file tu800-diagramu82esvgu800 file compiler-abstraktionu82esvgu800 file compiler-undu800-interpreteru82esvgu800 mediawiki aboutpage mediawiki aboutsite mediawiki backupcategories mediawiki_backupfiles mediawiki categorycloud mediawiki categorytree mediawiki commonu82ejsu800 mediawiki copyrightwarning mediawiki copyrightwarning2 mediawiki createpage mediawiki deletereason-dropdown mediawiki disclaimerpage mediawiki gadget-dantedump1u82ejsu800 mediawiki gadget-dantegadgettestu82ejsu800 mediawiki gadgets-definition mediawiki privacy mediawiki privacypage mediawiki sidebar mediawiki sidebar areas mediawiki sidebar categories mediawiki sidebar navigation mediawiki sidebar social mediawiki sidebar uiu800 mediawiki transitivebackupcategories template extension dplu800 template subpages category danteinitialcontents '),
(32,'danteinitialcustomize',' mediawiki copyright mediawiki copyrightnotice mediawiki danteintialcustomize project about project disclaimer project privacy information category danteinitialcustomize '),
(52,'parsifaltemplate preambletest',' defu800 iamapreamble iu800 amu800 au800 test ofu800 theu800 preamble feature category parsifaltemplate category danteinitialcontents category testpage '),
(7,'sidebar uiu800',' #tree extensions \"persist\" * javascript prtu800u82etogglelimitsize limit size * javascript prtu800u82etogglevariants show variants * javascript windowu82epersistcatwindow persist catu800 window category danteinitialcontents '),
(3,'parsifaltemplate beamer',' documentclass beamer begin document title simple beamer class author sascha frank date today begin document chcdisplayskipadjust typeout herestartsthemaindocument magic-line-identifier-foru800-inclusion endu800 document category parsifaltemplate category danteinitialcontents '),
(73,'empty',' this isu800 anu800 empty category category root category danteinitialcustomize category danteinitialcustomize '),
(74,'page belonging tou800 au800 nonu800-existant category',' category thisdoesnotexist '),
