(68,'danteinitialcontents',' this category contains pages used foru800 bootstrapping dantewiki.  important   weu800 strongly recommend that youu800 dou800 notu800 edit this category oru800 useu800 itu800 inu800 ownu800 pages asu800 this might break your system. this category isu800 au800  hidden category  itu800 does notu800 show onu800 theu800 pages itself however itu800 will show inu800 theu800 sidebar. __hiddencat__ category root '),
