(16,'dantelinks',' window * wu800 * fefe wu800 side * su800 * fefe su800  example  * main page doub * main page doub * main page doub * main page doub  example  * main page u8c2a6 style color green; * main page u8c2a6 style color green;  example  * help demo foru800 dantelinks u8c2a6 style color green; * help demo foru800 dantelinks u8c2a6 style color green;  example   adding style attributes tou800 anu800 external link viau800 broken pipe symbol * fefe u8c2a6 style color green; produces * fefe u8c2a6 style color green;  example   adding target attribute _blank tou800 anu800 external link opens itu800 inu800 au800 newu800 tabu800 * fefe u8c2a6 target _blank produces * fefe u8c2a6 target _blank foru800 useu800 inu800 sidebars only there isu800 au800 special class dexternal which canu800 beu800 used tou800 append anu800 external link symbol tou800 link. inu800 theu800 sidebar links which otherwise areu800 external will notu800 show theu800 symbol external. this isu800 asu800 weu800 need query extensions foru800 au800 number ofu800 links inu800 theu800 sidebar andu800 this needs fullurl asu800 parser andu800 this causes theu800 parser tou800 understand theu800 link asu800 external inu800 every case. therefore weu800 turned this thingie offu800 inu800 sidebar until weu800 find au800 smart fixu800 foru800 this. main page andu800 here main page some text fefe tou800 seeu800 theu800 distances when rendering inu800 text. requirements requirements requirements * weu800 always want tou800 seeu800 where au800 link goes internal oru800 external * weu800 always want tou800 know where au800 link opens same tabu800 newu800 tabu800 newu800 window * weu800 want tou800 allow theu800 user tou800 open theu800 link where heu800 wants tou800 same tabu800 newu800 tabu800 newu800 window * weu800 want tou800 force-open some links inu800 specific modes same tabu800 newu800 tabu800 newu800 window when theu800 user only clicks normally. allu800 link types allu800 link types allu800 link types 