(11,'parsifal cheat',' parsifal cheat sheet parsifal cheat sheet parsifal cheat sheet editor ifu800 theu800 editor frame window isu800 focused adjust theu800 font size ofu800 theu800 editor using cmdu800 oru800 cmdu800 - without resizing theu800 rest ofu800 theu800 browser. attributes attributes attributes collapse collapse collapse continuation continuation continuation situation weu800 want tou800 split texu800 text into several smaller portions. advantages ofu800 this areu800 * faster preview * smaller unit ofu800 error andu800 unit ofu800 editing * seperate edit link foru800 theu800 presentation there canu800 beu800 several scenarios * separation weu800 want au800 bitu800 ofu800 markup which lets theu800 reader seeu800 that there areu800 twou800 different portions ofu800 text. * continuation weu800 dou800 notu800 want tou800 indicate this separation into twou800 different portions ofu800 text. theu800 second portion should beu800 au800 seamless continuation ofu800 theu800 first text. nevertheless there should beu800 au800 possibility foru800 theu800 reader tou800 recognize theu800 twou800 parts andu800 tou800 invoke edit links andu800 similar actions foru800 theu800 twou800 parts. category danteinitialcontents '),
(5,'sidebar categories',' this page isu800 au800 system page. itu800 controls what isu800 shown inu800 theu800 categories portion ofu800 theu800 sidebar. theu800 contents ofu800 this page must conform tou800 theu800 following rules * theu800 page contains au800 single &ltu800;preu800 ... &ltu800; preu800 area. * this area contains au800 json data string ofu800 type array. * theu800 array contains objects ofu800 oneu800 ofu800 theu800 following types ** \"root\" \"depth\" ** \"name\" ** every object mayu800 contain anu800 optional \"style\" keyu800 whose value isu800 au800 cssu800 string. ** every object mayu800 contain anu800 optional \"classname\" field whose value refers tou800 au800 class name known tou800 theu800 system \"root\" \"root\" \"depth\" 4u800 \"name\" \"example\" \"style\" \"color redu800;\" \"name\" \"testpage\" \"style\" \"color green;\" category danteinitialcontents '),
