(53,'dantewiki faqu800',' faqu800 faqu800 faqu800 whyu800 isu800 this called dantewiki whyu800 isu800 this called dantewiki whyu800 isu800 this called dantewiki theu800 thought ofu800 writing done what oneu800 hasu800 understood dates back tou800 dante \"ou800 mente cheu800 scrivesti ciu8c3b2 chu8e28099io vidi\" dante inferno iiu800 8u800 \"ou800 gedu8c3a4chtnis dasu800 geschrieben wasu800 ichu800 erkannte\" ownu800 translation this thought hasu800 also been described inu800 au800 letter ofu800 nicolo machiavelli tou800 francesco vettori florentinian ambassador inu800 rome. weu800 cite itu800 here according tou800 niccolo machiavelli deru800 fu8c3bcrst. suhrkamp verlag 2016 undu800 weil dante sagt esu800 gebe keine wissenschaft ohne dieu800 aufzeichnung dessen wasu800 manu800 begriffen hatu800 u8e28093 sou800 habe ichu800 dasu800 notiert wasu800 ichu800 beiu800 demu800 gespru8c3a4ch mitu800 ihnen alsu800 dasu800 wesentliche festhielt undu800 einu800 kleines werk u8c3bcber fu8c3bcrstentu8c3bcmer verfau8c39ft worin ichu800 mich sou800 weit wieu800 mu8c3b6glich inu800 dieu800 gedanken u8c3bcber dieses thema vertiefe undu800 eru8c3b6rtere wasu800 herrschaft istu800 welche arten esu800 davon gibu800 wieu800 manu800 sieu800 erwirbt undu800 erhu8c3a4lt undu800 warum manu800 sieu800 verliert. oru800 foru800 short \" eu800 su800 gibt keine wissenschaft ohne dieu800 aufzeichnung dessen wasu800 manu800 begriffen hatu800.\" \"there isu800 nou800 science without au800 record ofu800 what oneu800 hasu800 understood\" ownu800 translation that that\'su800 whyu800 iu800 call this wiki system au800 dantewiki. what does theu800 logo show what does theu800 logo show what does theu800 logo show theu800 logo shows au800 painting made byu800 michelangelo merisi dau800 caravaggio inu800 1607. itu800 depicts saint jerome ofu800 stridon whou800 isu800 best known foru800 hisu800 translations ofu800 theu800 bible into latin. itu800 here serves asu800 theu800 symbol ofu800 au800 scientist philosopher andu800 thinker. saint jerome isu800 alone remote from theu800 distractions ofu800 theu800 world focused alone onu800 putting down hisu800 thoughts. theu800 skull onu800 hisu800 table reminds usu800 ofu800 theu800 mortality ofu800 manu800 andu800 theu800 volatility ofu800 hisu800 thoughts. itu800 thus challenges usu800 tou800 write down ouru800 thoughts. theu800 logo thus reflexts myu800 core motives when creating this system. what isu800 theu800 relation tou800 mediawiki what isu800 theu800 relation tou800 mediawiki what isu800 theu800 relation tou800 mediawiki none. iu800 didu800 notu800 want tou800 build this system completely from scratch. mediawiki wasu800 theu800 software which contained most ofu800 theu800 necessary base functionality andu800 wasu800 open foru800 further development dueu800 tou800 itsu800 open license model. iu800 will tryu800 tou800 keep dantewiki asu800 close tou800 mediawiki asu800 possible tou800 ease maintenence andu800 bugu800 fixing. what isu800 theu800 relation tou800 wikipedia what isu800 theu800 relation tou800 wikipedia what isu800 theu800 relation tou800 wikipedia none. while wikipedia isu800 au800 very interesting project iu800 dou800 notu800 subscribe tou800 theu800 objectivist perspective onu800 which itu800 seems tou800 beu800 grounded. inu800 particular - inu800 myu800 opinion - theu800 neutral point ofu800 view goal ofu800 wikipedia cannot beu800 achieved foru800 au800 number ofu800 linguistic reasons andu800 should notu800 beu800 aimed foru800 dueu800 tou800 au800 number ofu800 philosophic reasons. dantewiki follows different goals andu800 guidelines. category danteinitialcontents '),
