(55,'subpages',' special prefixindex 1u800 #ifu800 #translation basepagenamee fullpagenamee hideredirects 1u800 translate-hidetranslations ifu800 showtranslations 0u800 1u800 documentation content documentation subpage usage usage usage --tu800 1u800-- --tu800 2u800-- subpages shows allu800 theu800 subpages ofu800 au800 given page. itu800 should notu800 beu800 used inu800 theu800 main namespace only onu800 pages such asu800 user pages wiktionary pages andu800 appendices. itu800 takes oneu800 optional parameter theu800 target page name. theu800 default isu800 pagename * subpages shows theu800 subpages foru800 theu800 current page inu800 this case template subpages * subpages user example shows theu800 subpages foru800 user example alternative alternative alternative --tu800 3u800-- youu800 canu800 also embed theu800 special prefixindex directly eu800u82egu800. special prefixindex prefix user example hideredirects 1u800 stripprefix 1u800 ifu800 youu800 want useu800 inu800 your wiki au800 sorted lists ofu800 subpages oru800 getu800 counts ofu800 itu800 foru800 using inu800 templates youu800 mayu800 tryu800 extension llu800 extension subpagelist . example using ofu800 this seeu800 wiki code ofu800 template template pages . itu800 itu800\'su800 alternative solution without tagu800 tagu800 pages open foru800 pages ofu800 books from theu800 llu800 extension proofreadpage . this template generate iu800u82eeu800. content ofu800 page theu800 birch-bark roll 1906 kniha . itu800 isu800 solution  without  dependency onu800 theu800 luau800 modules. '),
