(85,'customize',' youu800 might want tou800 customize theu800 following pages * project privacy information * project about * project disclaimer * project imprint copyright customization copyright customization copyright customization mediawiki copyright contains au800 copyright notice which isu800 displayed inu800 theu800 footer ofu800 every page. mediawiki copyrightnotice contains au800 longer copyright notice when theu800 user clicks onu800 theu800 copyright icon onu800 theu800 right side inu800 theu800 footer. itu800 mayu800 also beu800 linked tou800 inu800 other places. mediawiki copyrightwarning isu800 displayed under theu800 edit boxu800 when editing au800 page. mediawiki copyrightwarning2 mayu800 beu800 displayed inu800 au800 number ofu800 places butu800 unfortunately theu800 mediawiki reference isu800 very unclear onu800 theu800 details. information information information theu800 footer mayu800 contain theu800 following links * privacy-link * about-link * disclaimer-link * imprint-link more information privacy-link privacy-link privacy-link * mediawiki privacy contains theu800 text foru800 theu800 privacy-link. * mediawiki privacypage contains theu800 name ofu800 theu800 wiki page tou800 which theu800 privacy-link links tou800. itu800 currently links tou800 project privacy about-link about-link about-link * mediawiki aboutsite contains theu800 text ofu800 theu800 about-link. * mediawiki aboutpage contains theu800 name ofu800 theu800 wiki page tou800 which theu800 about-link links tou800. itu800 currently links tou800 project about disclaimer-link disclaimer-link disclaimer-link * mediawiki disclaimers contains theu800 text ofu800 theu800 disclaimer-link. * mediawiki disclaimerpage contains theu800 name ofu800 theu800 wiki page tou800 which theu800 disclaimer-link links tou800. itu800 currently links tou800 project disclaimer category danteinitialcontents '),
