(98,'dantewiki concepts',' perpetual beta perpetual beta perpetual beta perpetual beta isu800 au800 general concept ofu800 webu800 2u800u82e0u800 inu800 which au800 service isu800 never considered complete oru800 finished butu800 permanently isu800 inu800 au800 preliminary oru800 draft iu800u82eeu800. beta status. this isu800 inevitable inu800 many webu800 2u800u82e0u800 services asu800 only during theu800 construction ofu800 theu800 system au800 better understanding ofu800 theu800 requirements emerges. bootstrapped development bootstrapped development bootstrapped development bootstrapped development isu800 common inu800 open knowledge management systems. theu800 system itself isu800 used foru800 documenting theu800 work with theu800 system asu800 itu800 isu800 done onu800 this page. throughout this process theu800 users andu800 developers learn about their knowledge management needs. user cou800-development user cou800-development user cou800-development theu800 system isu800 notu800 developed byu800 itu800 architects foru800 users butu800 byu800 au800 user foru800 theu800 needs ofu800 theu800 users. thus theu800 developers areu800 typical representatives ofu800 theu800 user community which avoids theu800 usual distance between developers andu800 users. category danteinitialcontents '),
