(12,'dante cheat',' dante links dante links dante links * provides au800 possibility tou800 addu800 attributes tou800 links. * ensures that links au800-elements with target ** _window open inu800 au800 separate window next tou800 theu800 browser ofu800 similar size ** _side open inu800 anu800 800x800 window left onu800 theu800 screen. * provide markup foru800 external links which open inu800 au800 separate window w3cu800 wu800 asu800 opposed tou800 w3cu800 dante tree dante tree dante tree * au800 shift-click onu800 tou800 au800 category link opens theu800 category window asu800 seperate popup window inu800 small size andu800 onu800 theu800 left ofu800 theu800 screen. this proved helpful foru800 quick deploy ofu800 au800 category window asu800 anu800 overview. * au800 shift-click onu800 au800 link into au800 portal heading opens anu800 edit window foru800 that portal content. category danteinitialcontents '),
(70,'root',' this isu800 au800 generic root category. category danteinitialcustomize '),
