(87,'\n[[Main Page ┬” target=_blank]]\n\n[[Main Page ┬” target=_new]]\n\n\n[[Help:Transclusion Test]]\n\n= Level 1 =\n\n\n<amsmath>\nBlabla this is an ekjhkjh kjhkjh kjhkjh kjhkjh xample for an entire line filling the entire area of the browser to get a demonstration for the autoscaling feature. \n</amsmath>\n\n== Level 1.1 ==\n\n=== Level 1.1.1 ===\n<amsmath>\nBlabla this is an example for an entire line filling the entire area of the browser to get a demonstration for the autoscaling feature.\n</amsmath>\n\n<amsmath>\nBlab wer qwer qwer qwer qwer qsdf sdf dsf sdf sdf sdf sdf df sdf er qwer qwer qwer qwer qwer qwer qerqwerqewrqerqerqewrqwerqwerqwer sdf sdfsdfsdfsdf sdfsdfsdfsdf sdfsdf gggggggggggggggggggggggggggggg ggggggggggggggggggsdf\n\n\\bigskip\\bigskip\\bigskip\n\nthis hjkhjk hjk hjk hjk hjk hjkhjk hjk hjk hjk hjkhjk\n\n\\bigskip\\bigskip\\bigskip\n\nis kjh hjk hjk\n\n\\bigskip\\bigskip\\bigskip\n\nan \n\n\\bigskip\\bigskip\\bigskip\n\n\nexample \n\n\\bigskip\\bigskip\\bigskip\n\n\nfor \n\nan \n\n\\bigskip\\bigskip\\bigskip\n\nentire line \n\n\\bigskip\\bigskip\\bigskip\n\nfilling \n\n\\bigskip\\bigskip\\bigskip\n\nthe \n\n\\bigskip\\bigskip\\bigskip\n\nentire \n\narea of the browser to get a demonstration for the autoscaling feature.\n</amsmath>\n\n\n==== Level 1.1.1.1 ====\n\n<amsmath>\n\\tikzdeg\n\\begin{figure} \n\\centering\n\\begin{tikzpicture}\n\\node (a) {E}\nchild {node (b) {F}\n}\nchild {node (c) {+}\n}\nchild {node (d) {T}\nchild {node (e) {T} \n  child {node (f) {F}  child {node  (g) {8}} }  \n  }\nchild {node  (h) {*}}\nchild {node  (i) {F} child {node  (j) {2}}}\n};\n\n\\begin{scope}[every node/.style={font=\\footnotesize,color=red}]\n\\node[right=of a] (na) {\\{E.v${}\\coloneqq{}$+T.v\\}};\n\\node[right=of d] (nd) {\\{T.v${}\\coloneqq{}$F.v$^{*}$T.v\\}};\n\\node[right=of i] (ni) {\\{F.v${}\\coloneqq{}$2\\}};\n\\node[left=of b] (nb) {\\{F.v${}\\coloneqq{}$5\\}};\n\\node[left=of e] (ne) {\\{T.v${}\\coloneqq{}$F.v\\}};\n\\node[left=of f] (nf) {\\{F.v${}\\coloneqq{}$8\\}};\n\\foreach \\i in {a,b,d,e,f,i}\n  \\draw[dotted] (\\i) -- (n\\i);\n\\end{scope}\n\\end{tikzpicture}\n\n\\end{figure}\nk hjhjk hjkhjk hj fgh fgh tzutzu\n</amsmath>\n\n===== Level 1.1.1.1.1 =====\n<amsmath sans>\nTest asd asd a aqqqqjhgjhgjhgjhgjhgjhgjhgjhgjhgjhgjhgjhgjhgj\nIch glaube es ist jetzt schon nicht so ganz einfach mit dem\nscheduling dessen, was wir im backendsehen. hjkjhj\n\n</amsmath>\n\n\n====== Level 1.1.1.1.1.1 ======\n\n======= Level 1.1.1.1.1.1.1 =======\n\n======== Level 1.1.1.1.1.1.1.1 ========\n\n== Level 1.2 ==\n\n=== Level 1.2.1 ===\n\n=== Lebel 1.2.2 ===\n\n== Level 1.3 ==\n\n=== Level 1.3.1 ===\n[[Category:DanteInitialContents]]','utf-8'),
