(90,'This page demonstrates and tests the styling of the heading, which happens\nin Parsifal/latex.css\n\n= h1 =\nIn h1  qw\n\n<amsmath sans>\n\\LaTeX In h1     \n   \n\\nonexistant\n\\noindent\\hrulefill\n</amsmath>\n\n== h2 ==\nIn h2\n\n<amsmath sans>\n\\LaTeX In h2\n\n\\noindent\\hrulefill   \n</amsmath>\n\n=== h3 ===\nIn h3\n\n<amsmath sans>\n\\LaTeX In h3\n\n\\noindent\\hrulefill\n</amsmath>\n\n==== h4 ====\nIn h4\n\n<amsmath sans>\n\\LaTeX In h4\n\n\\noindent\\hrulefill\n</amsmath>\n\n===== h5 =====\nIn h5\n\n<amsmath sans>\n\\LaTeX In h5\n\n\\noindent\\hrulefill\n</amsmath>\n\n====== h6 ======\nIn h6\n\n<amsmath sans>\n\\LaTeX In h6\n\n\\noindent\\hrulefill\n</amsmath>\n\n======= h7 =======\nIn h7\n\n<amsmath sans>\n\\LaTeX In h7\n\n%\\noindent\\hrulefill\n</amsmath>\n\n<amsmath sans>\nsecond element\n\n</amsmath>','utf-8'),
