(103,'Pages of the structure <code>Help:Test/*</code> contain tests.\n\nThey are part of the <code>Help:</code> namespace, since tests provide additional examples of how the system works.\n\n== List of <code style=\"font-size:smaller\">Help:Test/*</code></small> ==\n{{Special:PrefixIndex/Help:Test/}}\n\n== List of <code style=\"font-size:smaller\">Help:Test/Parsifal</code></small> ==\n{{Special:PrefixIndex/Help:Test/Parsifal}}','utf-8'),
(104,'\nThis is a test page for which there exists a corresponding page in the snip namespace.\n\nHere is the link to this corresponding page: [[Snip:Sniptest]]\n\nHere is the ssss ssss ssss sssss link to this corresponding page: [[Snip:Sniptest]]\n\nHere is a link to this page itself [[Sniptest]]\n\nHere is a link to a page linking to this page [[Sniptestlinker]]\n\n<snip i>XT snip.</snip>\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nx\n\nHere is the ssss ssss ssss sssss link to this corresponding page: [[Snip:Sniptest]]','utf-8'),
