(120,'This category contains all pages which may serve as templates for the Parsifal extension.\n\nUsually, such templates are also in the MediaWiki: namespace and subpages of [[MediaWiki:ParsifalTemplate]]\n[[Category:DanteInitialCustomize]]','utf-8'),
